Using a method similar to the synthesis of tert-butyl 2-(4-(phenyl(3-(trifluoromethyl)-phenyl)methyl)piperazin-1-yl)acetate, the following compounds were prepared.
tert-butyl 2-(4-((3,5-dichlorophenyl)(phenyl)methyl)piperazin-1-yl)acetate;
tert-butyl 2-(4-((4-chlorophenyl)(phenyl)methyl)piperazin-1-yl)acetate;
